# Exclude Unity YAML/assets from GitHub language stats
*.mat      -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.asset    -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.unity    -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.prefab   -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.anim     -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.controller -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.lighting -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.shadergraph -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.shadervariants -linguist-detectable linguist-generated
*.terrainlayer -linguist-detectable linguist-generated

# Keep C# counted
*.cs linguist-language=C#

# Ignore TutorialInfo layout files from language stats
*.wlt linguist-generated